{
  "id": "adv_card_mna_02_01",
  "title": "長瀬麻奈 1話 突然のプレゼント",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（麻奈は、東京レイーズでのライブを見事成功させた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mana successfully completed the live performance at Tokyo Reyes.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（俺は麻奈の体調を心配して、ライブの実施に）\n（反対していたが、幸いにも杞憂に終わった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I was worried about Mana's health and initially opposed the live performance.）\n（Fortunately‚ it turned out to be unnecessary worry.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（それでも、麻奈の健康を考えて）\n（一週間の休暇を取ることにしたのだが――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But still‚ considering Mana's health…）\n（I decided to give her a one-week vacation.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-11.m4a",
      "text": "レイーズのライブ、本当に盛り上がったよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The live at Reyes was really exciting‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-05.m4a",
      "text": "今までで最高の出来だったんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was the best performance we've ever had‚ wasn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、とても良かったよ。さすがだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it was really great. As expected of you‚ Mana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_mean-09.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん、私を誰だと思ってるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe‚ who do you think I am?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "……長瀬麻奈、だろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're Mana Nagase‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-07.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんだぞ！　凄いんだぞ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! I'm amazing‚ you know!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい。だから当然ってことだな\n観客動員記録も更新出来たし、良かったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ yeah. It's only natural.\nAnd we were able to break the attendance record too. That's great.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-03.m4a",
      "text": "記録？　何それ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Record? What's that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "デビュー後、東京レイーズを満員にしたアイドルとして\n麻奈は歴代最速だったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After your debut‚ as an idol who filled Tokyo Reyes to capacity…\nMana became the fastest in history.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "つい先日、LizNoirが作ったばかりの記録を\nすぐに更新したんだ。これは凄いことだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just recently‚ you immediately broke the record set by LizNoir.\nThat's amazing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_surp-03.m4a",
      "text": "ヘー、そうなんだ。でも、あんまり実感ないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ really? But I don't really feel it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_fan-01.m4a",
      "text": "私はファンのみんなの前で歌いたいだけだしね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just want to sing in front of all the fans‚ you know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "まるで他人事だな。あれ以来、こっちは\n仕事のオファーが倍増して調整で大変なのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's like it doesn't concern you. Since then‚\nwe've been getting twice the number of work offers‚ and it's been tough to coordinate…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_laughter-04.m4a",
      "text": "なら全部受けちゃいなよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then just accept them all!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "絶対ダメだ。もう麻奈を入院なんてさせないからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Absolutely not. I won't let you be hospitalized again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-01.m4a",
      "text": "相変わらず{user}くんは心配症だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As always‚ {user}‚ you worry too much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-08.m4a",
      "text": "ギリギリまで、ライブの開催に反対してたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were even against holding the live until the last moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前だろ、退院したばかりだったんだぞ\n……とにかく、明日から一週間きっちり休んでもらう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course. You had just been discharged from the hospital.\n…Anyway‚ starting from tomorrow‚ take a full week off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_sad-05.m4a",
      "text": "はーい、約束だし、仕方なく休みまーす",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ I promised. So I'll reluctantly take a break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "一応言っとくけど、ボイトレもダンスレッスンもダメ\n完全休養だからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just to make it clear‚ no vocal training or dance lessons either.\nIt's complete rest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-04.m4a",
      "text": "えーっ……レッスンは仕事じゃないから良くない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehh… But lessons aren't work‚ so it's fine‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンもダメ。これはお願いじゃない\n業務命令だ。守れなかったらペナルティが発生するぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lessons are also off-limits. This is not a request.\nIt's an order. If you don't comply‚ there will be penalties.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_angry-02.m4a",
      "text": "横暴だよ！　パワハラ！　労働基準法違反！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's overbearing! It's harassment! Violation of labor laws!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈が働き過ぎると違反になるんだからな？\n……ほら、これ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would be a violation if Mana works too much‚ right?\n…Here‚ take a look at this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.7,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4599.9999999999945,
          "startTime": 129.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_ask-09.m4a",
      "text": "……遊園地のチケット？　二枚ある……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…An amusement park ticket? There are two…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_surp-04.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　これって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Is this…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "たまには羽を伸ばして遊ぶのもいいと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought it would be nice to have some fun occasionally.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_02_01/sud_vo_adv_cmn_mna_glad-12.m4a",
      "text": "これに行こうって……こと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You mean…go here?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
